一島鏈，是美國應對大陸所設定，連結日本、菲律賓等的海上防線。"},{"pid":"c91b306e41e05d31051d4270a869d6e2671a6c0c","tid":2365374,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"拜燈表示可以賣"},{"pid":"304685b4bda3509d573a583085d1c02731c60a01","tid":2365374,"uid":14867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c91b306e41e05d31051d4270a869d6e2671a6c0c","tid":2365374,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"拜燈表示可以賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"台灣，香港，西藏，人權，民主，自由，有錢通通賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735a80dd48fce76e793d3d3c684a26907c6de8f4","tid":2365374,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb40faf90ec572f36b856ee2bdeda2020a0de8fb","tid":2365374,"uid":14867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"登粉入嚟一齊FF下兒登會點樣對抗中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a299960d3720f5c9c969f4d277370ea9a1ccc588","tid":2365374,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944523f55ed329e10b1f052d1fdc68ffb4b68382","tid":2365374,"uid":289900,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime